

I. GENERATING JSON WITH CONTROL FLOW GRAPH

    requirements: 
        - LLVM 5.0 (with opt tool), clang (older versions should work)
        http://releases.llvm.org/download.html#5.0.0

    For each .c file:
        1. Compile to .ll (LLVM IR)
        clang -S -emit-llvm file.c
        
        2. Extract control flow graph into json:
        opt -mem2reg -load=path/to/LLVMCFGextractor.dylib -extract_cfg file.ll -to-json file.json

    (Optional) VISUALIZE CFG
    opt -mem2reg -dot-cfg hello.ll (For each function in ll generates .dot.cfg file)
    dot -Tpng file.dot -o file.png (Generates PNG with visualized CFG of the function)


